creator: Hago Games
descriptionHtml:
HAGO is an all-in-one social media platform that caters to your every need! Have you been bored during quarantine? 😵Then be bored no more! Join us and stream 🤳, chat 💬, play 🎮, and share 📱 special moments in your life! 🤩


100+ FREE GAMES, ALL IN ONE
Come and have unlimited fun playing over 100 free games! Whether you're looking for an action-packed game, a mind-stimulating match, or just a cozy pastime, we got it all for you! You’ll never get bored. 🎮
Each round takes less than three minutes! Play with your friends now! 🤼
More and more excellent new games will continuously be added to our platform. Turn on your notification to make sure you don’t miss any updates! 🔔
NON-STOP LIVE STREAMS
Enjoy watching real-time concerts, lively dance performances, hilarious stand-up comedies, exciting e-sport competitions and many other awesome shows 24/7! 🎤
If you are a dance lover or an excellent singer, don’t hesitate to go live and show the world what you got! 🎶
Countless excellent streamers have become superstars on HAGO. You can become one of them! Make your name heard while earning money! 🤩
Support the hosts by giving them some of our many fun and delightful gifts! 🎁
Do you have any talent you wish to show the world? Join HAGO now and be the next big streamer! 🙌
SOCIALIZE WITH OLD AND NEW FRIENDS
Join the public chat room and meet new people! You can pick your interests, get matched, and build new friendships! 👭
Throw a karaoke party in the chat room, start a Draw Something competition, or hold an online voice chat party…There are so many fun things for you to explore on the app! 🤗
Video chat makes it possible to chat with your friends face-to-face anytime, anywhere! Enjoy the various filters and stickers that bring more fun to your call! 🗣️📱
Join now and socialize with your friends, old and new! ✨
SHARE SPECIAL MOMENTS
Share some of the special moments of your life on Square! You will find people of diversified interests. Say hello and make new friends! 👋
Quick casual game matches and profile matches are available to help you find new friends and easily break the ice! 🤝
What are you waiting for? Download the app and start sharing now! 🤩


STAY TUNED WITH US:
Official Website: https://ihago.net/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HagoGlobal
descriptionShort: HAGO - Play With New Friends

HAGO is an all-in-one social media platform that caters to your every need! Have you been bored during quarantine? 😵Then be bored no more! Join us and stream 🤳, chat 💬, play 🎮, and share 📱 special moments in your life! 🤩


100+ FREE GAMES, ALL IN ONE
Come and have unlimited fun playing over 100 free games! Whether you're looking for an action-packed game, a mind-stimulating match, or just a cozy pastime, we got it all for you! You’ll never get bored. 🎮
Each round takes less than three minutes! Play with your friends now! 🤼
More and more excellent new games will continuously be added to our platform. Turn on your notification to make sure you don’t miss any updates! 🔔
NON-STOP LIVE STREAMS
Enjoy watching real-time concerts, lively dance performances, hilarious stand-up comedies, exciting e-sport competitions and many other awesome shows 24/7! 🎤
If you are a dance lover or an excellent singer, don’t hesitate to go live and show the world what you got! 🎶
Countless excellent streamers have become superstars on HAGO. You can become one of them! Make your name heard while earning money! 🤩
Support the hosts by giving them some of our many fun and delightful gifts! 🎁
Do you have any talent you wish to show the world? Join HAGO now and be the next big streamer! 🙌
SOCIALIZE WITH OLD AND NEW FRIENDS
Join the public chat room and meet new people! You can pick your interests, get matched, and build new friendships! 👭
Throw a karaoke party in the chat room, start a Draw Something competition, or hold an online voice chat party…There are so many fun things for you to explore on the app! 🤗
Video chat makes it possible to chat with your friends face-to-face anytime, anywhere! Enjoy the various filters and stickers that bring more fun to your call! 🗣️📱
Join now and socialize with your friends, old and new! ✨
SHARE SPECIAL MOMENTS
Share some of the special moments of your life on Square! You will find people of diversified interests. Say hello and make new friends! 👋
Quick casual game matches and profile matches are available to help you find new friends and easily break the ice! 🤝
What are you waiting for? Download the app and start sharing now! 🤩

descriptionHtml:
At hago, you can discover new friends while enjoying games, video chat and stream. We proudly built this platform, so people can come together and hang out anytime, anywhere.

[100+ games for you to play]
Ranging from 1-on-1 competitions, to group-chat games, and to group-video games, there are over 100+ games you can play on Hago.

[Thousands of free chat rooms]
You can choose your favorite chat room from thousands of rooms and chat with people from all over the world on topics that interest you.

[Group chat]
Explore the public chat rooms from chill peeps or grab your squad for a private, invite-only online hangout.

[Share your happy moment on Square]
Our users share their lives on Square, from BBQ master to K-pop fan. We also offer instant quick casual game matches in Match and profile matches in Meetup for you to find new friends and to easily break the ice.

[Exciting stream rooms with different topics]
Come to Hago's stream rooms whenever you get bored. Tens of thousands of talented hosts are waiting for you. There are plenty of categories to choose from, like singing, dancing, cooking and more.

Join Hago to make new friends at ease.
Join Hago and interact with old friends.

At hago, you can discover new friends while enjoying games, video chat and stream. We proudly built this platform, so people can come together and hang out anytime, anywhere.

[100+ games for you to play]
Ranging from 1-on-1 competitions, to group-chat games, and to group-video games, there are over 100+ games you can play on Hago.

[Thousands of free chat rooms]
You can choose your favorite chat room from thousands of rooms and chat with people from all over the world on topics that interest you.

[Group chat]
Explore the public chat rooms from chill peeps or grab your squad for a private, invite-only online hangout.

[Share your happy moment on Square]
Our users share their lives on Square, from BBQ master to K-pop fan. We also offer instant quick casual game matches in Match and profile matches in Meetup for you to find new friends and to easily break the ice.

[Exciting stream rooms with different topics]
Come to Hago's stream rooms whenever you get bored. Tens of thousands of talented hosts are waiting for you. There are plenty of categories to choose from, like singing, dancing, cooking and more.

Join Hago to make new friends at ease.
Join Hago and interact with old friends.

Check out our sites and stay in touch with us
Website: https://ihago.net

Download Hago Now! Create your own party room and have a good online party here!

descriptionHtml:

[200+ Mini Games]
Hago has more than 200 mini games for you and your friends to play. Whether you're looking for Ghost dorm, ludo, brain teaser or you just want to chill, we've got you covered.

Download Hago Now! Create your own party room and have a good online party here!

creator: HAGO
descriptionHtml:
Hago provides you a way to party online with friends. Download Hago to enjoy chat rooms, online party games, live streams and have unlimited fun. Join Hago to have a good online party and hangout with friends anytime anywhere.

[Have A Good Online Party]
Hago is a best place for you to have online party with friends. Karaoke, gossip, wedding, or birthday parties, choose any theme you like. Great chance to surprise your friends with amazing gifts like cake, rose, crown etc.

[Watch live streams]
Check out talented streamers on Hago. Singing, dancing, makeup and more!

[Group Voice Chat Room] Join group voice chat room and hang out with friends. You can create/choose the theme of your room according to your interests. Come here to have a voice chat party!

[Online Party Games]
Looking for more indoor entertainment? Hago provides online party games for you and your friends to have a fun night.

[200+ Mini Games]
Hago has more than 200 mini games for you and your friends to play. Whether you're looking for Ghost dorm, ludo, brain teaser or you just want to chill, we've got you covered.

Download Hago Now! Create your own party room and have a good online party here!

Follow us & stay connected: Website: www.hago.sg
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HAGOUS/
Email: hagogamez@gmail.com
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@hago_us
